{"tid":1893368,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"小西灣屋苑授權票玩晒 一票佔28%業權 居民質疑造假","createTime":"2020-02-23T08:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T10:20:47.000Z","uid":135867,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fc9506aa568712c731ef260bb1ef2ec7b2a6894d","tid":1893368,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:20:14.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）早前，小西灣富怡花園業主立案法團管理委員會涉擅用達160萬港元屋苑儲備，支付主席楊漢成的官司訴訟費；法團亦被揭發六年來懶理修葺令，致整個屋苑被釘契。居民早前收集超過5%業主的簽署，並於1月5日提交予法團，要求其於45日內召開特別大會。<br />\n法團於昨日「死線」召開特別大會，過千人出席，佔全體業主46.1%。會議由晚上八時半開始至凌晨二時方結束，結果「罷免現屆管委會全體委員」及「反對替主席楊漢成支付官司的訴訟費及賠償」均被否決。點票時，一張含二萬九千多份業權的票遭居民質疑做假，楊漢成批評居民輸打贏要，強調自己公平公正行事，「我哋行得好正確，所有嘢都係真嘅」。居民要求驗票未遂，但表明會再召開特別業主大會及股東大會追討。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/news/localnews/小西灣屋苑授權票玩晒-一票佔28percent業權-居民質疑造假/ar-BB10gX9R?ocid=spartandhp \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fnews%2Flocalnews%2F%E5%B0%8F%E8%A5%BF%E7%81%A3%E5%B1%8B%E8%8B%91%E6%8E%88%E6%AC%8A%E7%A5%A8%E7%8E%A9%E6%99%92-%E4%B8%80%E7%A5%A8%E4%BD%9428percent%E6%A5%AD%E6%AC%8A-%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E9%80%A0%E5%81%87%2Far-BB10gX9R%3Focid%3Dspartandhp%20&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyoGpPR2DWAUw81xbwDiv9SI%3D&h=7e92e380\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/news/localnews/小西灣屋苑授權票玩晒-一票佔28percent業權-居民質疑造假/ar-BB10gX9R?ocid=spartandhp </a><br />\n<br />\n陌生黑衣大漢駐守平台 場內不准錄音拍攝<br />\n除一般工作人員外，大會亦安排數名黑衣大漢駐守平台維持秩序，並不時提醒居民「小心行」。有居民向本網記者指，從來沒有於苑內見過他們，不認為他們是居民，「喺邊度請返嚟？」更質疑是「黑社會」，「阿公阿婆見到都唔敢上嚟啦。」<br />\n大會亦要求場內人士不准錄音及拍攝，本網記者採訪期間，楊漢成斥「你都知我係邊個㗎啦，影嚟冇意思」，更謂「我唔想比你影得唔得呢？」"},{"pid":"f257d6166291291f512a53e2e202936b39c04f05","tid":1893368,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/styles/w775/public/column_images/fake_0.jpg?itok=i_YJqiNp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fw775%2Fpublic%2Fcolumn_images%2Ffake_0.jpg%3Fitok%3Di_YJqiNp&h=4dd42717&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/49568364813_bdfebc4cf5_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F49568364813_bdfebc4cf5_b.jpg&h=6eac123d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1070974\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1070974&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyoGpPR2DWAUw81xbwDiv9SI%3D&h=1fc2a474\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1070974&h=f45e33a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1070974</a><br />\n反對都係3萬幾,一票已經2萬9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇關<br />\n【決戰區選●景怡】擅用法團辦公室助選 小西灣景怡楊漢成涉公器私用<br />\n《蘋果》接到讀者投訴，指控小西灣景怡選區候選人楊漢成涉公器私用，利用富怡花園業主立案法團主席身份之便，未經住户同意下擅用法團辦公室助選。楊被發現後今晚（24日）一度被居民包圍，驚動屋苑保安員駐守辦公室外，又拒絕接受傳媒訪問。<br />\n<br />\n居於富怡花園24年的陳先生指，據居民了解，法團辦公室一向不對外借，但臨近選舉日，多名手持楊漢成選舉背心的助選團成員，竟於屋苑自出自入，曾進出法團辦公室取物資或去廁所等，惟管理處職員未有阻攔，直至有居民投訴才帶領助選團離開。他質疑，楊乘職權範圍之便擅用公家資源參選，不但對居民做成滋擾，亦漠視其他業主的知情權。<br />\n<br />\n楊漢成於2007年曾以民建聯身份出戰區議會，參選美孚南選區落敗，2011年報稱獨立，轉戰小西灣景怡選區，連續兩屆對戰工聯會和泛民候選人，惟議席都由工聯會梁國鴻奪得。雖然楊報稱獨立，但其申報地址為左派團體柴灣區街坊福利會。有居民收到楊的選舉廣告，聲稱獲前民主黨黨員、前景怡區議員陳耀德支持。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191124/U445PK7UTR4GIEKXVTNG7TQBMA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191124%2FU445PK7UTR4GIEKXVTNG7TQBMA%2F&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyoGpPR2DWAUw81xbwDiv9SI%3D&h=c752f4c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191124%2FU445PK7UTR4GIEKXVTNG7TQBMA%2F&h=3486ca82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191124/U445PK7UTR4GIEKXVTNG7TQBMA/</a>"},{"pid":"60378e06283d949db2cd6fd6b859ed3de963d99b","tid":1893368,"uid":160268,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:28:39.000Z","msg":"根本佢就係比人追擊<br />\n想坐佢位cap油水"},{"pid":"1292a5f1db72e719f666bcaa19fea22cc87f76f0","tid":1893368,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:29:46.000Z","msg":"咁佢d 票係真定假"},{"pid":"6bb65b9085a265ed04162f3f5ea3ed8f3508206a","tid":1893368,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QF4mHri.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQF4mHri.jpg&h=e2211196&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41009487be373ebbbb52edd2bdfd85a3e5156c6e","tid":1893368,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:31:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/74376818_600581680684128_1463894325296365568_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_ohc=AbcEl08twHMAX9DFZUy&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=3cef2dbf5be5ae53e56130e060b7d608&amp;oe=5EB57CE0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F74376818_600581680684128_1463894325296365568_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_ohc%3DAbcEl08twHMAX9DFZUy%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D3cef2dbf5be5ae53e56130e060b7d608%26oe%3D5EB57CE0&h=528e04b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=600581677350795&amp;set=gm.1181227782060997&amp;type=3&amp;theater&amp;ifg=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D600581677350795%26set%3Dgm.1181227782060997%26type%3D3%26theater%26ifg%3D1&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyoGpPR2DWAUw81xbwDiv9SI%3D&h=9c7e3904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=600581677350795&amp;set=gm.1181227782060997&amp;type=3&amp;theater&amp;ifg=1</a>"},{"pid":"2dd4fc3ddc280f63353567b28c9a0fe894578189","tid":1893368,"uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"60378e06283d949db2cd6fd6b859ed3de963d99b","tid":1893368,"uid":160268,"like":5,"dislike":