票俾現任法團<br />\n所以根本唔出席就唔應該有投票權</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"68b06f3ac369cf65a66c7adedbb379fcc2cca1d8","tid":1893368,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T09:17:49.000Z","msg":"暴力可以解決一切問題"},{"pid":"cfed35dc2e4c43f0282e236e80418c200ad27b20","tid":1893368,"uid":276440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T09:24:35.000Z","msg":"其實開會前24小時已經要做晒委任代表的文書(即係授權票)，而且亦會有張list貼出嚟公司邊戶人做咗授權票。<br />\n<br />\n身為業主其實好應該深入了解《建築物管理條例》(CAP 344)"},{"pid":"740dc82436a27caf038dfd186d8bf611c5dfcc08","tid":1893368,"uid":153929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9eddbdec4946364c23503b4b8dd2c5a0a60fce4e","tid":1893368,"uid":13100,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"26513e7d2383d638c970203304b19221e029c974","tid":1893368,"uid":153929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:44:09.000Z","msg":"點解1票有28%？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"我估係好多個單位業主授權俾某一個出席者,所以舉一隻手=28%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果啲授權書係真,咁有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T10:07:33.000Z","msg":"嗯.<br />\n不過我試過自己個屋苑投票, 有人假冒咗我家人簽名寫授權書, 我去到現場登記先知. 我要求check返張授權書個簽名見只係打咗個交叉, 問家人話無簽過. 諗緊點追究."},{"pid":"cee685e95081d0dd8db7c6dd6e23f9ad76b61ebf","tid":1893368,"uid":89869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"740dc82436a27caf038dfd186d8bf611c5dfcc08","tid":1893368,"uid":153929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9eddbde